An Application that will record and total the score

Vision: An application that will help the scorer in their job

Mission: Create an application that will record and display the score

Feature:
    Record score,total score, display score - it will record, total,  display the score of each team
     

 User story:
     As a user, I want to record ,total, and display the score of each team.

 Use case:
Name: Record the score
Description: It will record the score of each team
Actor: User
Pre-Conditions:it has two teams
Post-Conditions: the user will be able to record the score
Main Course:
1. the user will input the score 
2. the system will record the score
3. the system will total the score
4. the system will display the score
 